column5: CT store has the 550 Humminbird fishfinder , reg 199.99 , on sale for 119.99 .
I'm not a humminbird fan but it'll get you started. There are no major problems with the unit. I find that it's underpowered but for $119, go for it.
I have one for my bow mount... It's a good unit...  I can mark my jig in 60 FOW...

I have this unit, but I cant for life of me read it. I have no idea what im looking at other then the fish markers. I would like to be able to know what things mean...Perhaps I should buck up and get a better one this spring
